CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

February 18, 2005

[Cite as 02/18/2005 Case Announcements, 2005-Ohio-637.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2004-1945. State ex rel. Rittner v. Dennis.

Williams App. No. WM-04-009, 2004-Ohio-5679. This cause came on for further consideration of appellant’s motion to order Warden Jessie Williams to extend credit in order to access this court. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion be, and hereby is, denied.
